Movie.create!({:genres=>[], :title=>"Mas allá del Mall", :overview=>"Is there an audience for Latin American movies? These are some of the questions posed by an Ecuadorian filmmaker whose latest movie was a commercial flop. He embarks on a query to find answers to his questions and relief for his despair. His research leads him to a giant contraband market in the port city of Guayaquil, where pirated movies from all over the world are sold for one dollar each. Here, he discovers a number of Ecuadorian low budget movies produced by amateurs, with titles he had never heard of before: from action packed productions to evangelical melodramas.", :poster_path=>"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/4uvDpDox31zfjcq2bFtrHwPAKzI.jpg", :release_date=>"2010-11-09"})
